tle eye-candy with their monitors will be happy to know that there is RGB lighting on the rear, along with an Asus logo that can project onto your desk if that's what you're into. Overall, you really can't go wrong with this monitor and now that it's down to its lowest price, it's an absolute no-brainer. So get it now before the deal's over.",
