ly, you\u0026#39;ll also be able to adjust the height, tilt, and even pivot of the monitor. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThose that like a little eye-candy with their monitors will be happy to know that there is RGB lighting on the rear, along with an Asus logo that can project onto your desk if that\u0026#39;s what you\u0026#39;re into. Overall, you really can\u0026#39;t go wrong with this monitor and now that it\u0026#39;s down to its lowest price, it\u0026#39;s an absolute no-brainer. So get it now before the deal\u0026#39;s over. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
